4. Now that the key chain has been created, issue the following commands on Router3 to enable EIGRP authentication using the new key chain. Note that the EIGRP neighbor relationship between Router3 and Router4 is restored.Router3(config)#interface serial 0/1
   Router3(config-if)#ip authentication mode eigrp 100 md5
   Router3(config-if)#ip authentication key-chain eigrp 100 ccna-chain

